    Hit the dirt as Colin McRae Rally, the ultimate off-road racing game
    experience, returns to PC
    From the developers of the multi-million selling franchise and based

    Focus. Pace notes read by professional rally co-driver Nicky Grist

    With the critically acclaimed Colin McRae Rally handling, damage and

    Take on different game modes including quick races, full rallies and
